.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-1-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, fanta, iced-tea, mirinda
There 4 different types of food: pumpkin, spinach, tomato, zucchini
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, scooter, skateboard, bike
1. the person drinking mirinda is the person driving the bike##1
2. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person eating spinach##1
4. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
5. the person eating tomato is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
7. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | fanta    | iced-tea | mirinda | 7up        |
| Food       | zucchini | pumpkin  | spinach | tomato     |
| Transport        | scooter    | skateboard   | bike  | jet-ski |

