3. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
4. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
5. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the car##1
6. the person driving the airplane is on the left of the videographer##1
7. the person who growsbegonia is the person driving the scooter##1
8. the person who growszinnia is the bartender##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |      2       |       3       |       4       |
| Job         | bartender  | videographer | photographer  | social-worker |
| Flower       | zinnia | amaryllis        | balloon-flower | begonia       |
| Transport   | airplane   | car          | tram          | scooter       |

