1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
2. the person watching mystery movies is the owner of the hamster##1
3. the spanish is on the left of the canadian##1
4. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
5. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
6. the owner of the hedgehog is the pakistani##1
7. the spanish is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Pet         | horse   | dog   | hedgehog | hamster |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | adventure | disaster   | mystery |
| Nationality   | spanish     | canadian  | pakistani  | german  |

