1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the fan of trance##1
2. the person drinking milk is the fan of trance##1
3. the person who's hobby is reading is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
4. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
5. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the fan of metal##1
6. the person drinking milk is on the left of the fan of blues##1
7. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4    |
| Hobby         | traveling | chess    | baking        | reading |
| Music-Genre   | metal     | rock     | trance        | blues   |
| Beverage         | iced-tea   | coffee | milk | 7up  |

