3. the person who's sport is tennis is on the far right##1
4. the pakistani is on the far right##1
5. the indonesian is the person who's sport is parkour##1
6. the russian is on the far left##1
7. the person who growszinnia is on the far right##1
8. the russian is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |       4        |
| Flower           | lily  | marigold  | amaryllis | zinnia |
| Nationality   | russian   | indonesian | nigerian   | pakistani      |
| Sport         | badminton | parkour    | biathlon   | tennis         |

 